## Customizing this template

This file is generated from `templates/run-readme.md.template` at the repo root.

**To change the default cover page** for all future runs, edit that template. Available substitutions:

| Token | What it becomes |
|---|---|
| `{{slug}}` | Run slug (e.g. `vector-db-comparison-2026`) |
| `{{status}}` | `Final` / `In progress` / `Revised` |
| `{{date}}` | Run date `YYYY-MM-DD` |
| `{{complexity}}` | `simple` / `comparison` / `complex` |
| `{{query_one_line}}` | One-line query restatement |
| `{{tldr_block}}` | The TL;DR block from `synthesis.md`, copied verbatim |
| `{{optional_sections}}` | Reserved for per-domain extensions (e.g. comparison matrix preview, decision summary) |

**To override per-run** (rare): write `templates/run-readme-<slug>.md.template`. The lead-researcher will pick the most-specific match. Keep the standard template the default.
